	function Polyvalue = POLY_AT_X(Poly, x) 	%	Evaluates the value of a polnomial, Poly, with the highest power first, at x 	%	using Horners method. 	% Toolbox for  DIGITAL FILTERS USING MATLAB 		% Author: 			Lars Wanhammar, 1983-03-15	% Modified by:		LW 2006-01-12, 2007-07-24	%	Copyright:		by authors - not released for commercial use	% Version: 			1	% Known bugs:	 	% Report bugs to:	Wanhammar@gmail.com		Polyvalue =  0;	for j = 1:length(Poly)		Polyvalue = x*Polyvalue + Poly(j);	end